    17	/**
    18	 * Logs in through the real staff auth path — POST /api/v1/auth/login/ followed by
    19	 * GET /api/v1/auth/me/ — by driving the login form. It never injects tokens or
    20	 * mocks the backend, so the suite fails if the login call is bypassed (002EY req 7).
