+## Source / Review References
+
+- `docs/source/screen-spec.md` S21 and S23
+- `docs/source/api-contracts.md` §§6.2, 8.1, 25.3, and 25.9
+- `docs/source/codebase-design.md` §§23.3-23.5, 26.1-26.3, and 42.3
