Architecture review completed successfully for `220f3038...e1698e87`, covering slices 007R, 007S, 008A2, and 008B. No production, protected, or source files were modified.

The independent Standards and Spec passes found:

- Standards: 2 High and 2 Medium issues, primarily the reversed legal-document dependency boundary and module-level authority bypass.
- Spec: 2 High, 2 Medium, and 1 Low issue, including the legacy S23 null-shape crash, stale post-action refreshes, and insufficient DOCX/PDF content proof.
